===Background===
Minisa was born into [[House Whent]] and married [[Hoster Tully]], the head of [[House Tully]] and [[Lord of Riverrun]]. They had two daughters, [[Catelyn Stark|Catleyn]] and [[Lysa Arryn|Lysa]], and a son and heir, [[Edmure Tully|Edmure]].&lt;ref name=&quot;House Tully viewers guide&quot;&gt;[http://viewers-guide.hbo.com/game-of-thrones/season2/#!/guide/houses/tully/ HBO viewers guide, season 2 guide to houses, House Tully entry]&lt;/ref&gt;
===[[Season 2]]===
When [[Brienne of Tarth]] mentions she never knew her mother, Catelyn sympathizes and tells her own mother died in childbirth when Catelyn was still a young girl.&lt;ref&gt;[[The Ghost of Harrenhal]]&lt;/ref&gt;
